What you need to know:  AK president Jack Tuwei disclosed Thursday that the first athlete to cross the finish line in their respective final in the two-day trials will book an automatic ticket to the world junior eventThe program looks exciting with nine medallists from the last 2021 Nairobi World Under-20 Athletics Championships contesting for places in the team that will be named SaturdayWith defending champion Emmanuel Wanyonyi qualifying for the World Championships and Commonwealth Games, Noah Kibet from North Rift, who claimed bronze medal in 800m at the world junior event, is a sure bet